        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued April 4 at 12:54AM CDT until April 4 at 1:30AM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 1254 AM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 20 miles south of
Garden City, moving northeast at 50 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
southeastern Glasscock and northeastern Reagan Counties.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
